items.name: Garden Salad (Serves 8-20)
items.description: Small serves 8-10 sides. Large serves 16-20 sides. Romaine lettuce, shredded red cabbage, tomatoes, cucumber and shredded cheddar cheese. Served with your choice of dressing and croutons on the side. Includes serving utensils.

items.name: Greek Salad (Serves 8-20)
items.description: Small serves 8-10 sides. Large serves 16-20 sides. Chopped romaine topped with chicken breast, feta cheese, tomatoes, red onions, Kalamata olives and cucumeber. Served with our Roasted Garlic Vinaigrette on the side and includes serving utensils.

items.name: Birthday Cake - Catering Only (Serves 10)
items.description: Serves 10. Celebrate your birthday with Portillo's homemade chocolate cake topped with Portillo's candles! Kit includes one Chocolate Cake and one package of Portillo's candles. Party decorations not included.

items.name: Chocolate Cake (Serves 1)
items.description: Serves 1. Not just rich, but famous too! 9-inch round, two layer chcolate cake with LOTS of chocolate fudge frosting. Made fresh daily. Store at room temperature.

items.name: Chopped Salad (Serves 1)
items.description: Small serves 1. Large serves 2 side. Chopped romaine, iceberg lettuce and red cabbage with diced chicken breast, ditalini pasta, bacon, tomatoes, Gorgonzola cheese and green onion. Served with our House Dressing on the side and includes serving utensils.

items.name: Cheese Sauce (Serves 5)
items.description: Serves 5. Our famous cheese sauce served family-style. Enough for the French Fry Fast Pack or Onion Ring Fast Pack order.

items.name: Italian Beef & Sausages (Serves 8)
items.description: Serves 8, makes 16 half sandwiches. Sandwiches featuring the combination of our char-grilled sausage and Chicago's #1 Italian beef on perfectly baked French bread, served with easy gravy and cut in half. Sweet & Hot Peppers included.

items.name: Chicago Style Hot Dogs (Serves 8)
items.description: Serves 8. All beef hot dogs served plain on poppyseed buns, with all toppings on the side. Condiments include: mustard, relish, celery salt, freshly chopped onions, sliced red ripe tomatoes, kosher pickle, and sport peppers.

items.name: Caesar Salad - Catering Only (Serves 8-20)
items.description: Small serves 8-10 sides. Large serves 16-20 sides. Crisp romaine, parmesan cheese and croutons. Served with our Caesar Dressing on the side and includes serving utensils.

items.name: Plant-based Garden Dogs (Serves 8)
items.description: Serves 8. Plant-based hot dogs served plain on poppy seed buns, with all toppings on the side. Made with 100% plant-based protein. The Garden Dog is crafted for Portillo's by Field Roast. Condiments include: mustard, relish, celery salt, freshly chopped onions, sliced red ripe tomatoes, kosher pickle, and sport peppers.
